        <t:body>
            <t:div type="bibliography">
                <t:listBibl type="editions">
                    <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/TD2UJDSH"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:MeckelburgSolomon2017Antislavery"/><title level="a">Ethiopia and Great Britain: A Note on the Anti-Slavery Protocol of 1884</title><title level="j">Northeast African Studies</title><author><t:forename>Alexander</t:forename><t:surname>Meckelburg</t:surname></author><author><t:name>Solomon Gebreyes Beyene</t:name></author><date>2017</date><biblScope unit="volume">17</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">2</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">61-82</biblScope><note type="url">https://www.jstor.org/stable/10.14321/nortafristud.17.2.0061?seq=1</note></t:bibl>
                    
                </t:listBibl>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="edition" xml:lang="am"> 
                
                <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="1">
                    <t:ab>
                  <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9745Victoria">ቢክቶርያ፡</t:persName> በጸጋ፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3697egziabe">እግዚአብሔር፡</t:persName> 
                        የታላቋ፡ <t:placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q23666">ብርታንያና፡</t:placeName>
                        <t:placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1672441">የአይርለንድ፡</t:placeName> 
                  <t:roleName type="title">ንግሥት፡ </t:roleName>የ
                        <t:placeName ref="50004">ህንደኬ፡</t:placeName> ቂሳርይት፡ 
                        ሥዩመ፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3697egziabe">እግዚአብሔር፡</t:persName>
                  <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10378Yohanne"> ዮሐንስ፡</t:persName>
                        ንጉሠ፡ ጽዮን፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10378Yohanne">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ንጉሠ፡  ነገሥት፡ </t:roleName> 
                  </t:persName>ዘ
                        <t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3010Ethiop">ኢትዮጵያ፡</t:placeName> ወኵሉ፡ አድያሚሃ፡</t:ab>
                </t:div>
                <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="2">
                    <t:ab>በ<t:placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q23666">እንግሊዝ፡</t:placeName> ቤተ፡ መንግሥትና፡ በ<t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3010Ethiop">ኢትዮጵያ፡</t:placeName>
                        ቤተ፡ መንግሥት፡ የባሪያ፡ ንግድ፡ እንዲቀር፡ ባሪያ፡ እንዳይሼጥ፡ በፈቃዳችን፡ ተዋደን፡ 
                        ውል፡ አድርገናል፡ ለዘለዓለም፡ በ<t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3010Ethiop">ኢትዮጵያ</t:placeName>ና፡ በ<t:placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q23666">እንግሊዝ፡</t:placeName> መንግሥት፡ ለነገሠ፡ ይህን፡ ነገር፡ ሊጨርስ፡ የመጣ፡ ምስለኔአችን፡
                        <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5320Hewett">ሪየር፡ አድሚራል፡ ሰር፡ ውሌም፡ ሕወት፡</t:persName> 
                        የ<t:placeName ref="50004">ህንደኬ፡</t:placeName> ጦር፡ መርከብ፡ ደምሳሺ፡ ነው፡ ከታላቋ፡ <t:placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q23666">ብርታንያና፡</t:placeName>
                        ከ<t:persName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1672441">የአይርለንድ፡</t:persName> 
                  <t:roleName type="title">ንግሥት፡ </t:roleName> የ<t:placeName ref="50004">ህንደኬ፡ </t:placeName>
                        ቂሳርይት፡ የተላከ፡ መቅድም፡ </t:ab>
                </t:div>
                <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="3">
                    <t:ab>[፩] <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10378Yohanne">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ጃንሆይ፡ </t:roleName> 
                  </t:persName> በግዛትዎ፡  ባሪያ፡ እንዳይሼጥ፡ እንዳይለወጥ፡ ሊከለክሉ፡ 
                        [፪] <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10378Yohanne">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ጃንሆይ፡ </t:roleName>
                     <t:roleName type="title">ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ </t:roleName> 
                  </t:persName> 
                        ዘ<t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3010Ethiop">ኢትዮጵያ፡</t:placeName> ባሪያ፡ ከሌላ፡ አገርም፡
                        መጥቶ፡ ካገ[ር]ዎ፡  ከግዛ[ት]ዎም፡  እንዳይሼጥ፡ እንዳይለወጥ፡ ወደ፡ ሌላ፡ አገርም፡ ወጥቶም፡ እንዳይሼጥ፡ ይህን፡ ወደው፡  ውል፡ አድርገናል
                        [፫] <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10378Yohanne">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ጃንሆይ፡ </t:roleName>
                     <t:roleName type="title">ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ </t:roleName> 
                  </t:persName>
                        ዘ<t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3010Ethiop">ኢትዮጵያ፡</t:placeName> ነጣ፡ የወጣ፡ ባሪያ፡ ወደ፡ ባርነት፡ እመልሰዋለሁ፡ ብሎ ፡ የያዘው፡ እንደሆን፡ በብርቱ፡ ቅጣት፡ ሊቀጣ፡ ፈቅደዋል፡
                        [፬] የ<t:placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q23666">ብርታንያና፡</t:placeName>
                  <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9745Victoria">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ንግሥት፡ </t:roleName> 
                        </t:persName> ከሌሎች፡ ነገሥታት፡ ጋራ፡ ሁሉ፡ ባርያ፡ እንዳይሼጥ፡ ቀድሞ፡ ውል፡ አድርጋለች፡ ስለዚህ፡ በባሕር፡ ያሉ፡ ሹማምቶችዋን፡ ጠብቁ፡ ብላ፡ አዛለች፡ በመርከብ፡ ሲሄድ፡ ባርያ፡ ቢያገኙ፡ እንዲይዙ፡ 
                        ደግሞ፡ በመርከብ፡ ላይ፡ የሀበሻ፡ ሰው፡ ባርያ፡ ተብሎ፡ ቢያዝ፡ ወደ፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10378Yohanne">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ </t:roleName> 
                  </t:persName> 
                        ወደ፡ አገሩ፡ ይመለስ፡ ብላ፡ ንግሥት፡ አዛለች
                        [፭] ይህ፡ የእርቅ፡  ውል፡ ቶሎ፡ ብሎ፡ ታትሞ፡ <t:placeName when="1884" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC1264Adwa">አድዋ፡</t:placeName> ድረስ፡ ይመጣል፡ ደግሞ፡ ስለ፡ ምስክርነት፡
                        <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5320Hewett">ሪየር፡ አድሚራል፡ ሰር፡ ውሌም፡ ሕወት፡</t:persName> 
                        የ<t:placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q23666">ብርታንያና፡</t:placeName> 
                  <t:persName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1672441">የአይርለንድ፡</t:persName> ንግሥት፡
                        የ<t:placeName ref="50004">ህንደኬ፡</t:placeName> ቂሳርይት፡ ምስለኔና፡
                        ሥዩመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10378Yohanne"> ዮሐንስ፡</t:persName>
                        ንጉሠ፡ ጽዮን፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10378Yohanne">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡</t:roleName> 
                  </t:persName>ዘ
                        <t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3010Ethiop">ኢትዮጵያ፡</t:placeName> ለዚህ፡ ውል፡ ሁለቱም፡ በገዛ፡ እጃቼው፡ ማኅተማቼውን፡ አትመዋል፡ </t:ab>
                </t:div>
                <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="4">
                    <t:ab>ተጽሕፈ፡ በ<t:placeName when="1884" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC1264Adwa">አድዋ፡</t:placeName> ከተማ፡ አመ፡ ካልኡ፡ ለጁን፡ በ፲ወ፰፻፹ወ፬ ዓመተ፡ 
                        ምሕረት፡ በ<t:placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q23666">እንግሊዝ፡</t:placeName> ቊጥር፡ በ፲ወ፰፻፸ወ፮፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ አመ፡ ፩ለሰኔ፡
                        በ<t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3010Ethiop">ኢትዮጵያ፡</t:placeName> ቊጥር፡
                        
                    </t:ab>
                </t:div>
                   </t:div>
            
            
        </t:body>
    </t:text></TEI>